window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The flames of war are rising.</b></p> <p>David has everything to fight for and more to lose. With two fierce wives by his side and loyal allies at his back, David heads to the volcanic hellscape of Elpis to face off against the Kuro.</p> <p>But the planet’s not the only thing that’s making him sweat.</p> <p>As alien foes close in, David must balance leadership, survival, and the pull of hearts that refuse to stay quiet. Tensions flare on and off the battlefield.</p> <p>Unfortunately, David's responsibilities won't wait for his love life to sort itself out.</p> <p>Secrets about the Kuro emerge—ones that could shift the tide of the war and shape David’s future. With change inevitable and passion simmering just beneath the surface, there’s no room for hesitation.</p>"; 
